<p><a href="/scp-4623">SCP-4623: The Bard (Owl) of England</a> (<span style="color: green">+31</span>, <span style="color: firebrick"><sup>&#8230;</sup>4</span>)<br />
<span style="font-size:80%;"><span style="color: grey"><em>Created on <span class="odate time_1584709177 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">20 Mar 2020 12:59</span></em></span></span></p>
</div>
    
    
    
    </div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶&nbsp;COMMENTARY</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷&nbsp;COMMENTARY</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>I'll admit it, my main motivation for making this SCP was to make a pun on my username. It was also my first attempt at a comedy-type article.</p>
<p>When I was first ideating about making this article, I originally wanted to make it about the owl and a junior researcher (her name was going to be Naomi Green or something like that) gradually coming to tolerate each other. As the owl gradually gave up the act of being William Shakespeare, the researcher would soon learn to have a warm spot for the fellow. I think the owl was supposed to attack one of the researchers by poking out their eye with their beak. Oh yeah, and the owl was supposed to <em>talk</em>. (shudder)</p>
<p>Anyway, after that, I started leaning into the group of interest storyline. Originally, the person chosen to become an owl was an unwilling participant, a businessman captured from off the streets, who gets more and more confused about his eventual fate of getting turned into an owl. However, in my drafts of this idea, I changed it into a more willing participant (a friend of the ritual setter), which made the storyline a lot less confusing and a lot more realistic (I mean, about as realistic as you could make a guy about to be transformed into an owl).</p>
<p>There are some parts which I do think could do with some cleaning up in the future, such as the incident log, but overall, I'm happy with the finished product. I do have to give due respect to the critters of this when it was still being drafted, who I will list here:</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Draft Critters:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4057128); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4057128); return false;">Alces_alces</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5336470); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5336470); return false;">cybersqyd</a></span>, DrUnoriginal, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rioludoodle" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3165531); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3165531&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="rioludoodle" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3165531)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rioludoodle" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3165531); return false;">rioludoodle</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;">RockTeethMothEyes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zoobeeny" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6070624); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6070624&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="Zoobeeny" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6070624)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zoobeeny" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6070624); return false;">Zoobeeny</a></span></p>
<p><strong>Special Thanks:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(455145); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=455145&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="Petrograd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=455145)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(455145); return false;">Petrograd</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span> for convincing me to finally publish the article!</p>
