<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Yeah, I only drew the picture for this, but it certainly was nice to be working with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="RJB_R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;">RJB_R</a></span>. I'm actually not too familiar with the Technical Researcher Rosen character &#8212; I was going for more of a 90's feel (i.e. the Amiga keyboard, the beige palette), so it was kind of a surprise to see that Rosen was supposedly employed in 2012. Anyway, it was a great honor to be working with Roget for the brief time I could.</p>
